.PP
Synopsis

.EX
tfctl si [RootDir]

.EE

.PP
Short description

.PP
Start an interactive console to explore state data (search resources, run ad-hoc queries, and view results inline).

.PP
Flags and related docs

.RS
.IP \(bu 2
See the common flag reference: Flags
\[la]../flags.md\[ra]
.IP \(bu 2
Attributes: Attributes
\[la]../attrs.md\[ra]

.RE

.PP
Quick examples

.EX
# Start interactive console in CWD
 tfctl si

# Exit the console
 Type `exit` or press Ctrl+C

.EE

.PP
Notes

.RS
.IP \(bu 2
\fBsi\fR uses a terminal UI and stores history in \fB~/.tfctl_si_history\fR\&.
.IP \(bu 2
For scripted/extractable output, prefer \fBsq --output json\fR\&.

.RE

